          "reviewBody": "It’s been more than 10 years here I’m in 12th grade. All the teaching and non teaching staffs are great, humble and Are always there for students. Principal mam is really cooperative and student’s well being has always been her priority. This Gives lots of opportunities to the students to showcase their talent and also helps to develop their personality. All the teachers are really talented and have a great experience in their particular subjects. This school provides a friendly atmosphere to the students and makes learning fun and interesting. We have won many trophies and medals in all these years on inter school, state levels etc. Literally had a great experience here.\nBest CBSE school in Kharadi",
